<p>
  This is PLUCS, it brings instant messaging to your domain.

  <ul>
    <li>
      It installs a Jabber (XMPP) service to your host, allowing
      users to communicate over the XMPP protocol.
    </li>
    <li>
      It adds some controls to the Management Console, allowing you
      to manage the service as well as groups and users.
    </li>
  </ul>
</p>
